[
  {
    "bundleId": "b0",
    "bundleIndex": 0,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-0.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-0.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "At sixty-four years old, Grace stood on the beach in Florida, looking across the water toward Cuba.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 6.96,
        "duration": 6.96,
        "sentenceIndex": 0
      },
      {
        "text": "She had first tried to swim this distance thirty-five years earlier, when she was twenty-eight.",
        "startTime": 6.96,
        "endTime": 13.501,
        "duration": 6.541,
        "sentenceIndex": 1
      },
      {
        "text": "She had failed then, and she had not swum a single stroke for thirty years after that.",
        "startTime": 13.501,
        "endTime": 19.437,
        "duration": 5.936,
        "sentenceIndex": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "But now, at sixty-four, she was about to try again.",
        "startTime": 19.437,
        "endTime": 23.168,
        "duration": 3.731,
        "sentenceIndex": 3
      },
      {
        "text": "Grace had been a champion swimmer in her twenties.",
        "startTime": 23.168,
        "endTime": 26.532,
        "duration": 3.364,
        "sentenceIndex": 4
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 26.531519,
    "measuredDuration": 26.531519
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b1",
    "bundleIndex": 1,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-1.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-1.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She had swum around Manhattan Island.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.678,
        "duration": 2.678,
        "sentenceIndex": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "She had swum between the Bahamas and Florida.",
        "startTime": 2.678,
        "endTime": 5.935,
        "duration": 3.257,
        "sentenceIndex": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "She had set records and become famous around the world.",
        "startTime": 5.935,
        "endTime": 9.916,
        "duration": 3.981,
        "sentenceIndex": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "But the Cuba swim was different.",
        "startTime": 9.916,
        "endTime": 12.232,
        "duration": 2.316,
        "sentenceIndex": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "It was not about sports or records.",
        "startTime": 12.232,
        "endTime": 14.766,
        "duration": 2.533,
        "sentenceIndex": 9
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 14.765714,
    "measuredDuration": 14.765714
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b2",
    "bundleIndex": 2,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-2.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-2.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "It was about a dream that would not let her go.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.294,
        "duration": 3.294,
        "sentenceIndex": 10
      },
      {
        "text": "When Grace was a child, she had a poster in her room.",
        "startTime": 3.294,
        "endTime": 7.159,
        "duration": 3.865,
        "sentenceIndex": 11
      },
      {
        "text": "It said, \"A diamond is a lump of coal that stuck with it.\" She had always valued perseverance.",
        "startTime": 7.159,
        "endTime": 13.897,
        "duration": 6.738,
        "sentenceIndex": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "She had always believed in never giving up.",
        "startTime": 13.897,
        "endTime": 16.911,
        "duration": 3.014,
        "sentenceIndex": 13
      },
      {
        "text": "But after failing the Cuba swim at twenty-eight, she had given up swimming completely.",
        "startTime": 16.911,
        "endTime": 23.088,
        "duration": 6.178,
        "sentenceIndex": 14
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 23.088322,
    "measuredDuration": 23.088322
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b3",
    "bundleIndex": 3,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-3.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-3.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "For thirty years, Grace worked as a sports journalist.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.851,
        "duration": 3.851,
        "sentenceIndex": 15
      },
      {
        "text": "She traveled to the Olympic Games.",
        "startTime": 3.851,
        "endTime": 6.181,
        "duration": 2.33,
        "sentenceIndex": 16
      },
      {
        "text": "She covered the Tour de France.",
        "startTime": 6.181,
        "endTime": 8.306,
        "duration": 2.125,
        "sentenceIndex": 17
      },
      {
        "text": "She wrote about the best athletes in the world.",
        "startTime": 8.306,
        "endTime": 11.527,
        "duration": 3.221,
        "sentenceIndex": 18
      },
      {
        "text": "It was a good life, but something was missing.",
        "startTime": 11.527,
        "endTime": 14.83,
        "duration": 3.303,
        "sentenceIndex": 19
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 14.829841,
    "measuredDuration": 14.829841
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b4",
    "bundleIndex": 4,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-4.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-4.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "As she approached sixty, she realized she was no longer a doer.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.882,
        "duration": 4.882,
        "sentenceIndex": 20
      },
      {
        "text": "She was only watching others do things.",
        "startTime": 4.882,
        "endTime": 7.811,
        "duration": 2.929,
        "sentenceIndex": 21
      },
      {
        "text": "She was bothered by this.",
        "startTime": 7.811,
        "endTime": 9.689,
        "duration": 1.878,
        "sentenceIndex": 22
      },
      {
        "text": "Grace decided to return to swimming.",
        "startTime": 9.689,
        "endTime": 12.392,
        "duration": 2.704,
        "sentenceIndex": 23
      },
      {
        "text": "She decided to chase her dream again, even though everyone said it was impossible.",
        "startTime": 12.392,
        "endTime": 18.701,
        "duration": 6.309,
        "sentenceIndex": 24
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 18.701224,
    "measuredDuration": 18.701224
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b5",
    "bundleIndex": 5,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-5.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-5.mp3",
    "sentences": [
