        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.046,
        "duration": 2.046,
        "sentenceIndex": 25
      },
      {
        "text": "Her body was older.",
        "startTime": 2.046,
        "endTime": 3.666,
        "duration": 1.62,
        "sentenceIndex": 26
      },
      {
        "text": "Her muscles were weaker.",
        "startTime": 3.666,
        "endTime": 5.713,
        "duration": 2.046,
        "sentenceIndex": 27
      },
      {
        "text": "But her dream was still alive.",
        "startTime": 5.713,
        "endTime": 8.271,
        "duration": 2.558,
        "sentenceIndex": 28
      },
      {
        "text": "The first attempt failed.",
        "startTime": 8.271,
        "endTime": 10.403,
        "duration": 2.132,
        "sentenceIndex": 29
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 10.402608,
    "measuredDuration": 10.402608
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b6",
    "bundleIndex": 6,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-6.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-6.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "The second attempt failed.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 1.871,
        "duration": 1.871,
        "sentenceIndex": 30
      },
      {
        "text": "The third attempt failed.",
        "startTime": 1.871,
        "endTime": 3.671,
        "duration": 1.799,
        "sentenceIndex": 31
      },
      {
        "text": "The fourth attempt failed.",
        "startTime": 3.671,
        "endTime": 5.542,
        "duration": 1.871,
        "sentenceIndex": 32
      },
      {
        "text": "Each failure was painful.",
        "startTime": 5.542,
        "endTime": 7.341,
        "duration": 1.799,
        "sentenceIndex": 33
      },
      {
        "text": "Each failure made people say she should give up.",
        "startTime": 7.341,
        "endTime": 10.796,
        "duration": 3.455,
        "sentenceIndex": 34
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 10.795873,
    "measuredDuration": 10.795873
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b7",
    "bundleIndex": 7,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-7.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-7.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "But Grace remembered her poster.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.336,
        "duration": 2.336,
        "sentenceIndex": 35
      },
      {
        "text": "A diamond is a lump of coal that stuck with it.",
        "startTime": 2.336,
        "endTime": 5.766,
        "duration": 3.43,
        "sentenceIndex": 36
      },
      {
        "text": "She would stick with it.",
        "startTime": 5.766,
        "endTime": 7.517,
        "duration": 1.752,
        "sentenceIndex": 37
      },
      {
        "text": "On the fifth attempt, Grace was sixty-four years old.",
        "startTime": 7.517,
        "endTime": 11.536,
        "duration": 4.018,
        "sentenceIndex": 38
      },
      {
        "text": "She swam for fifty-three hours straight.",
        "startTime": 11.536,
        "endTime": 14.455,
        "duration": 2.919,
        "sentenceIndex": 39
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 14.455011,
    "measuredDuration": 14.455011
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b8",
    "bundleIndex": 8,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-8.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-8.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She swam one hundred and ten miles through dangerous waters.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.419,
        "duration": 4.419,
        "sentenceIndex": 40
      },
      {
        "text": "Sharks swam nearby.",
        "startTime": 4.419,
        "endTime": 5.818,
