        "startTime": 5.818,
        "endTime": 7.291,
        "duration": 1.473,
        "sentenceIndex": 42
      },
      {
        "text": "The sun burned her skin.",
        "startTime": 7.291,
        "endTime": 9.059,
        "duration": 1.768,
        "sentenceIndex": 43
      },
      {
        "text": "But she kept swimming.",
        "startTime": 9.059,
        "endTime": 10.679,
        "duration": 1.62,
        "sentenceIndex": 44
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 10.67907,
    "measuredDuration": 10.67907
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b9",
    "bundleIndex": 9,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-9.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-9.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "When Grace finally reached the beach in Florida, thousands of people were waiting.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 6.154,
        "duration": 6.154,
        "sentenceIndex": 45
      },
      {
        "text": "They were crying.",
        "startTime": 6.154,
        "endTime": 7.398,
        "duration": 1.245,
        "sentenceIndex": 46
      },
      {
        "text": "They were emotional.",
