        "endTime": 8.862,
        "duration": 1.464,
        "sentenceIndex": 47
      },
      {
        "text": "These were not sports fans.",
        "startTime": 8.862,
        "endTime": 10.839,
        "duration": 1.977,
        "sentenceIndex": 48
      },
      {
        "text": "These were people who had watched Grace live out her message: Never ever give up.",
        "startTime": 10.839,
        "endTime": 16.97,
        "duration": 6.13,
        "sentenceIndex": 49
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 16.969615,
    "measuredDuration": 16.969615
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b10",
    "bundleIndex": 10,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-10.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-10.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Grace had been afraid her entire life of wasting her one wild and precious life.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 6.493,
        "duration": 6.493,
        "sentenceIndex": 50
      },
      {
        "text": "She had refused to let her life slip by.",
        "startTime": 6.493,
        "endTime": 9.739,
        "duration": 3.246,
        "sentenceIndex": 51
      },
      {
        "text": "She had determined to live a bold and fierce adventure.",
        "startTime": 9.739,
        "endTime": 14.202,
        "duration": 4.464,
        "sentenceIndex": 52
      },
      {
        "text": "And she had done it.",
        "startTime": 14.202,
        "endTime": 15.826,
        "duration": 1.623,
        "sentenceIndex": 53
      },
      {
        "text": "At sixty-four, she had proved that dreams do not expire.",
        "startTime": 15.826,
        "endTime": 20.52,
        "duration": 4.695,
        "sentenceIndex": 54
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 20.520272,
    "measuredDuration": 20.520272
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b11",
    "bundleIndex": 11,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-11.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-11.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Age is just a number.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 1.443,
        "duration": 1.443,
        "sentenceIndex": 55
      },
      {
        "text": "But Grace's story was not only about swimming.",
        "startTime": 1.443,
        "endTime": 4.605,
        "duration": 3.162,
        "sentenceIndex": 56
      },
      {
        "text": "It was also about learning.",
        "startTime": 4.605,
        "endTime": 6.461,
        "duration": 1.856,
        "sentenceIndex": 57
      },
      {
        "text": "When Grace was younger, she had wanted to finish her education.",
        "startTime": 6.461,
        "endTime": 10.941,
        "duration": 4.48,
        "sentenceIndex": 58
      },
      {
        "text": "She had started college, but life got in the way.",
        "startTime": 10.941,
        "endTime": 14.459,
        "duration": 3.518,
        "sentenceIndex": 59
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 14.459025,
    "measuredDuration": 14.459025
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b12",
    "bundleIndex": 12,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-12.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-12.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She had to drop out to help her family.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.675,
        "duration": 2.675,
        "sentenceIndex": 60
      },
      {
        "text": "She went on to have a successful career, but she always regretted not finishing her degree.",
        "startTime": 2.675,
        "endTime": 9.067,
        "duration": 6.392,
        "sentenceIndex": 61
      },
      {
        "text": "As Grace got older, she thought it was probably too late.",
        "startTime": 9.067,
        "endTime": 13.126,
        "duration": 4.06,
        "sentenceIndex": 62
      },
      {
        "text": "She put her education dreams behind her.",
        "startTime": 13.126,
        "endTime": 15.87,
        "duration": 2.744,
        "sentenceIndex": 63
      },
      {
        "text": "She got so involved in working and making a living that her dreams went out the window.",
        "startTime": 15.87,
        "endTime": 21.837,
        "duration": 5.967,
        "sentenceIndex": 64
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.837256,
    "measuredDuration": 21.837256
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b13",
    "bundleIndex": 13,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-13.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-13.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "But after completing the Cuba swim, Grace realized something important.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5.758,
        "duration": 5.758,
        "sentenceIndex": 65
      },
      {
        "text": "It is never too late.",
        "startTime": 5.758,
        "endTime": 7.416,
        "duration": 1.659,
        "sentenceIndex": 66
      },
      {
        "text": "Grace decided to go back to school.",
        "startTime": 7.416,
        "endTime": 10.181,
        "duration": 2.764,
        "sentenceIndex": 67
      },
      {
        "text": "At sixty-five, she enrolled in college classes.",
        "startTime": 10.181,
        "endTime": 14.043,
        "duration": 3.862,
        "sentenceIndex": 68
      },
      {
        "text": "She sat in classrooms with students who were younger than her own children.",
        "startTime": 14.043,
        "endTime": 19.967,
        "duration": 5.924,
        "sentenceIndex": 69
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 19.966757,
    "measuredDuration": 19.966757
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b14",
    "bundleIndex": 14,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-14.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-14.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Some of them looked at her strangely.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.154,
        "duration": 3.154,
        "sentenceIndex": 70
      },
      {
        "text": "Some of them asked why she was there.",
        "startTime": 3.154,
        "endTime": 6.307,
        "duration": 3.154,
        "sentenceIndex": 71
      },
      {
        "text": "But Grace did not care what they thought.",
        "startTime": 6.307,
        "endTime": 9.802,
        "duration": 3.495,
        "sentenceIndex": 72
      },
      {
        "text": "She was there to learn.",
        "startTime": 9.802,
        "endTime": 11.762,
        "duration": 1.96,
        "sentenceIndex": 73
      },
      {
        "text": "The classes were difficult.",
        "startTime": 11.762,
        "endTime": 14.063,
        "duration": 2.301,
        "sentenceIndex": 74
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 14.063401,
    "measuredDuration": 14.063401
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b15",
    "bundleIndex": 15,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-15.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-15.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Grace's mind was not as sharp as it had been when she was twenty.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.74,
        "duration": 4.74,
        "sentenceIndex": 75
      },
      {
        "text": "She had to study harder.",
        "startTime": 4.74,
        "endTime": 6.491,
        "duration": 1.75,
        "sentenceIndex": 76
      },
      {
        "text": "She had to work longer hours.",
        "startTime": 6.491,
        "endTime": 8.606,
        "duration": 2.115,
        "sentenceIndex": 77
      },
      {
        "text": "But she did not give up.",
        "startTime": 8.606,
        "endTime": 10.356,
        "duration": 1.75,
        "sentenceIndex": 78
      },
      {
        "text": "She remembered her swimming journey.",
        "startTime": 10.356,
        "endTime": 12.981,
        "duration": 2.625,
        "sentenceIndex": 79
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 12.981247,
    "measuredDuration": 12.981247
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b16",
    "bundleIndex": 16,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-16.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-16.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She remembered that perseverance was what mattered most.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.117,
        "duration": 4.117,
        "sentenceIndex": 80
      },
      {
        "text": "After four years of study, Grace graduated from college.",
        "startTime": 4.117,
        "endTime": 8.384,
        "duration": 4.267,
        "sentenceIndex": 81
      },
      {
        "text": "She was sixty-nine years old.",
        "startTime": 8.384,
        "endTime": 10.516,
        "duration": 2.132,
        "sentenceIndex": 82
      },
      {
        "text": "Her family threw her a surprise graduation party.",
        "startTime": 10.516,
        "endTime": 14.118,
        "duration": 3.602,
        "sentenceIndex": 83
      },
      {
        "text": "They invited all her friends.",
        "startTime": 14.118,
        "endTime": 16.25,
        "duration": 2.132,
        "sentenceIndex": 84
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 16.250385,
    "measuredDuration": 16.250385
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b17",
    "bundleIndex": 17,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-17.mp3",
    "audioPath": "age-defiance-1/A2/bundle-17.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "They gave her a cap and gown.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.148,
