        "endTime": 4.235,
        "duration": 2.369,
        "sentenceIndex": 151
      },
      {
        "text": "She said, \"If ever there was an anti-aging pill, you would have to call it exercise.\" She said, \"It is never too late to get healthy.",
        "startTime": 4.235,
        "endTime": 14.231,
        "duration": 9.996,
        "sentenceIndex": 152
      },
      {
        "text": "It is never too late to change your life.\"\n\nGrace's story shows us many things.",
        "startTime": 14.231,
        "endTime": 19.902,
        "duration": 5.67,
        "sentenceIndex": 153
      },
      {
        "text": "It shows us that dreams do not expire.",
        "startTime": 19.902,
