        "sentenceIndex": 161
      },
      {
        "text": "When Grace was sixty-four, she completed a swim that had defeated her at twenty-eight.",
        "startTime": 8.809,
        "endTime": 14.823,
        "duration": 6.014,
        "sentenceIndex": 162
      },
      {
        "text": "When she was sixty-nine, she graduated from college.",
