        "sentenceIndex": 166
      },
      {
        "text": "If you believe in your dream, if it is worthy of your precious time, if you just do not give up, you will get there.",
        "startTime": 8.907,
        "endTime": 17.917,
        "duration": 9.01,
        "sentenceIndex": 167
